{"id":909,"date":"2022-01-25T17:41:00","date_gmt":"2022-01-25T17:41:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=909"},"modified":"2022-01-24T14:59:06","modified_gmt":"2022-01-24T14:59:06","slug":"manage-tuning-profiles","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/?p=909","title":{"rendered":"Manage tuning profiles"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This will be a very short post, because in my opinion this is not used very often and doesn&#8217;t do much, but according to <a href=\"https:\/\/access.redhat.com\/documentation\/en-us\/red_hat_enterprise_linux\/7\/html\/performance_tuning_guide\/sect-red_hat_enterprise_linux-performance_tuning_guide-performance_monitoring_tools-tuned_and_tuned_adm\"><strong>RH site<\/strong> <\/a>and <a href=\"https:\/\/access.redhat.com\/videos\/898563\">this demo<\/a> it does so let&#8217;s get into it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The\u00a0<strong>tuned<\/strong>\u00a0tuning service can adapt the operating system to perform better under certain workloads by setting a tuning profile. The\u00a0<strong>tuned-adm<\/strong>\u00a0command-line tool allows users to switch between different tuning profiles.<\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Several pre-defined profiles are included for common use cases, but\u00a0<strong>tuned<\/strong>\u00a0also enables you to define custom profiles, which can be either based on one of the pre-defined profiles, or defined from scratch. In Red\u00a0Hat Enterprise\u00a0Linux\u00a07, the default profile is\u00a0<code>throughput-performance<\/code>.The profiles provided with\u00a0<strong>tuned<\/strong>\u00a0are divided into two categories: power-saving profiles, and performance-boosting profiles. The performance-boosting profiles include profiles focus on the following aspects:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>low latency for storage and network<\/li><li>high throughput for storage and network<\/li><li>virtual machine performance<\/li><li>virtualization host performance<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>So we are going to work with a utility called &#8220;tuned&#8221;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"83\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-176.png?resize=640%2C83&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-910\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-176.png?w=915&amp;ssl=1 915w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-176.png?resize=300%2C39&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-176.png?resize=768%2C99&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-176.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-176.png?resize=36%2C5&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-176.png?resize=48%2C6&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We can list all possible profiles with<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">tuned-adm list<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"273\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-177.png?resize=640%2C273&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-911\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-177.png?w=951&amp;ssl=1 951w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-177.png?resize=300%2C128&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-177.png?resize=768%2C327&amp;ssl=1 768w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-177.png?resize=24%2C10&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-177.png?resize=36%2C15&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-177.png?resize=48%2C20&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To check which profile is active right now we simply type<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">tuned-adm active<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"527\" height=\"61\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-178.png?resize=527%2C61&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-912\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-178.png?w=527&amp;ssl=1 527w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-178.png?resize=300%2C35&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-178.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-178.png?resize=36%2C4&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-178.png?resize=48%2C6&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 527px) 100vw, 527px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And because we are using virtual machine, it&#8217;s most likely going to be virual-guest.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We can check which one is recommended to us by the system<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">tuned-adm recommend<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-style-default\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"542\" height=\"63\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-179.png?resize=542%2C63&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-913\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-179.png?w=542&amp;ssl=1 542w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-179.png?resize=300%2C35&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-179.png?resize=24%2C3&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-179.png?resize=36%2C4&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-179.png?resize=48%2C6&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 542px) 100vw, 542px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And it&#8217;s again going to be most likely the same which was already active.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To make our tuning profile active and reboot proofed, we use this command with the profile we would like to use.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\">tuned-adm desktop<\/pre>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image is-style-default\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"574\" height=\"90\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-180.png?resize=574%2C90&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-914\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-180.png?w=574&amp;ssl=1 574w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-180.png?resize=300%2C47&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-180.png?resize=24%2C4&amp;ssl=1 24w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-180.png?resize=36%2C6&amp;ssl=1 36w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/image-180.png?resize=48%2C8&amp;ssl=1 48w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 574px) 100vw, 574px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This will be a very short post, because in my opinion this is not used [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":840,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"nf_dc_page":"","om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[219],"tags":[343,345,347,346],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/thetechcorner.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/rhsa-operate-running-systems.png?fit=1280%2C720&ssl=1","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/909"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fcomments&post=909"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/909\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":915,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/posts\/909\/revisions\/915"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/media\/840"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/thetechcorner.org\/index.php?rest_route=%2Fwp%2Fv2%2Fmedia&parent=909"}],"wp:term":[{"t